                     <interp inst="t18281023-93-verdict550" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>. Aged 20.</p>
               <p>Recommended to Mercy by the Jury. - <rs id="t18281023-93-punish551" type="punishmentDescription">
